    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Transform. Gamble. Survive</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Transform into bizarre octopus forms – a rapid-fire shooter, a time-stopping menace, a healing form, or a lightning-fast speedster – and fight your way through 20 increasingly brutal levels. Each transformation changes how you play. Every portal is a risk. And the clock is always ticking.<br> <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3146620/extras/318812e00ccab6080f7726419a6424e6.poster.avif?t=1770474352\" width=1170 height=660 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3146620/extras/318812e00ccab6080f7726419a6424e6.webm?t=1770474352\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3146620/extras/318812e00ccab6080f7726419a6424e6.mp4?t=1770474352\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >PICK YOUR FORM, PLAY YOUR WAY</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Build your deck of three octopus transformations. Switch between them mid-fight—need range? Go shooter. Surrounded? Freeze time. Low health? Shift to healer. But here's the catch: once you use a slot, it shuffles to a random new form. Adapt or die.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3146620/extras/19c4b80941cc72cb9a47ff226f3a6315.poster.avif?t=1770474352\" width=1170 height=660 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3146620/extras/19c4b80941cc72cb9a47ff226f3a6315.webm?t=1770474352\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3146620/extras/19c4b80941cc72cb9a47ff226f3a6315.mp4?t=1770474352\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >THE PORTAL GAMBLE</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each level hides multiple portals. Only one will lead you safely to the next level – the others will cause damage. Kill enemies, collect keys, open portals, and choose wisely. But don't take too long: hesitate and the safe portal disappears, leaving only painful options.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3146620/extras/5e847ce26b50dd9174738fd8dd0aeb18.poster.avif?t=1770474352\" width=1170 height=660 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3146620/extras/5e847ce26b50dd9174738fd8dd0aeb18.webm?t=1770474352\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3146620/extras/5e847ce26b50dd9174738fd8dd0aeb18.mp4?t=1770474352\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >UNLOCK YOUR ARSENAL</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Beat level 20 and permanently unlock new Transformation Orbs for future runs. Every victory expands your deck further. Collect them all – from the straightforward to the very bizarre ones.</p>",
